api_list.description:
Return a button configuration with `bid_id` parameter.  Add this new button on your website or app using the following js :
```
<script>
var s=document.createElement("script");
s.setAttribute("class","snapcall");
s.setAttribute("btn-id","bid_id returned-by-the-endpoint");
s.src="https://snap.snapcall.io/snapapp.min.js";document.body.appendChild(s);</script>
```
